snippet.title: Retro Map Jam 6: Egyptian Theme, part 1
snippet.description:
"Tombs of Tehuti" by Bloodshot, and "Within the Sands of Time" by Breezeep

Played on Quakespasm, and recorded with OBS over Youtube Gaming!

https://www.quaddicted.com/reviews/retrojam6.html

I’m playin’ this blind! Lets stare at some walls!

This is a collection of Egyptian Theme maps!
Lovecraftian horrors have invaded the Pyramids? Whatever shall we doooooooo!

---

This is a slow-paced "Let Play" with little commentary.
